sentences: Louis Mario Freese (born June 2, 1970), known by his stage name B-Real, is an American rapper.
Since 1991, he has been one of two lead rappers in the hip hop group Cypress Hill, along with Sen Dog.
He has also been a part of the rap metal band Kush (2000–2002), the hip hop supergroup Serial Killers (2013-present) and the rap rock supergroup Prophets of Rage (2016–2019).
